n$\\gamma_p-\\theta_B$ parameter space, and therefore conclude that the generation\nof FRBs in magnetar magnetosphere passes this test.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Apr 2022 22:48:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Jul 2022 05:18:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 4 Oct 2022 22:11:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-06"}
