ompressed model almost comes with no\naccuracy loss, and even outperforms its uncompressed counterpart in most cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 23 Apr 2022 15:33:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-26"}
